# Antigravity Rules — pointer file

This file used to duplicate ~70% of `AGENTS.md`. To keep the agent context
small (fewer tokens loaded into every session), the canonical rules now live
in a single place:

→ Read **`AGENTS.md`** as the single source of truth for coding standards,
  safety guardrails, MCP usage, and sub-agent coordination.

The Memory Bank entry points are still:

- `docs/INDEX.md` — map of every doc and when to load it.
- `docs/activeContext.md` — what's in flight right now (read on start).
- `docs/techContext.md` — stack/architecture (read on start, only relevant
  sections).
- `PROJECT_KNOWLEDGE.md` — business rules (read on start).

Historical/archive material lives under `docs/archive/` and should NOT be
loaded automatically.
